verbose_text: Two 51p1 IGHV1-69 Abs with germline V-segments and available unbound crystal structures, 1-69/B3, and 3B4, were expressed as scFv-phagemid Abs and were found to bind G6/hG6.3 stronger than D80 in MSD ELISA assay (data not shown).
